    "sidebarcontent": "[section:lore-box] [center][h2]Dramatis Personae[/h2][/center]\r\n\r\n[ul][li]@[Sahira Asrani](person:bf785367-4496-4868-8f1c-3cca9d094092): Sahira is a gnome with dark, wild hair, and a wide smile. She recently took over as head of the Asrani family business, Asrani Noodles. The weight of the new responsibility hangs heavy on her, but she is determined to make her family proud.[/li][/ul]\r\n[ul][li]@[Basim Jadari](person:041bb09c-0d99-4560-b80d-75fd539b0189): Basim is a kobold who dresses in impeccable purple-and-gold silk gowns and has polished horns. She runs a respected market stand, Jadari Seafood, and seeks to expand her family's business. She cheries her son, Gammon, whom she's teaching to take over the business.[/li][/ul]\r\n[/section]",
